{"tid":2077690,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方昨日於元朗塘頭埔村拘捕一名中年男子 涉嫌無牌管有槍械","createTime":"2020-06-24T12:42:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T14:20:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"858a6d497a58a5e070734b2ccccaf0fa5f1cb1d0","tid":2077690,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:42:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/weatherjj/26915\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fweatherjj%2F26915&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPiLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=6ccd4570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/weatherjj/26915</a><br />\n<br />\n警方邊界警區見記者，稱近日接獲情報指有人於網上售賣武器。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日於元朗塘頭埔村拘捕一名中年男子，並於其村屋搜獲弓弩、鐵蓮花、刀器、高強度雷射筆等數百件物品。被捕人士涉嫌干犯管有攻擊性武器、管有違禁武器及無牌管有槍械三罪。<br />\n<br />\n警方指未有資料顯示武器於近日示威被使用，但會沿此方向繼續調查，特別是買家的背景。<br />\n<br />\n#香港新聞"},{"pid":"6762b0bc0d158edf32e3dc49216bf34eab735ecd","tid":2077690,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442141825524f13b9f13b698c1e80fe8d9d4b63d","tid":2077690,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:49:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6671bfe63e26f5d2de2b90c7c4dccaf257d76d86","tid":2077690,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:50:05.000Z","msg":"建聯幫"},{"pid":"74382f0f5a28cef3c923a585c2a2e5e259953538","tid":2077690,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:53:12.000Z","msg":"好明顯係老黑啦屌"},{"pid":"28067b11adc8de6115776b6f07204050b7169821","tid":2077690,"uid":232157,"like":